nacos-client-2.0.3的
com.alibaba.nacos.client.naming.core.ServiceInfoUpdateService内部的UpdateTask的run方法，当serviceObj.getLastRefTime() <= lastRefTime会去查询服务对象，此时返回的服务对象的host为0，进而publish的event内部的host列表也是0，最后在consumer上更新实例会因为是空host产生空的instance，consumer端会无法正常下线生产者服务

```
if (serviceObj.getLastRefTime() <= lastRefTime) {
    serviceObj = namingClientProxy.queryInstancesOfService(serviceName, groupName, clusters, 0, false); <==   此处返回空host列表的服务对象
    serviceInfoHolder.processServiceInfo(serviceObj);
}
```

